26	avalon_20251201_003138	Bob	evil	evil	proposal	100400	100400	\N	This team keeps the Alice–Charlie failed pair completely off the mission while building around the emerging consensus that Diana is the most trusted player so far. Using Diana + Bob as the core respects Diana’s preference not to auto-clear Eve while still incorporating my own earlier stance that Diana + Eve looked like the strongest base; adding me gives the table a fresh, still-untested slot rather than reusing someone from the failed M3 team. Including Eve over Alice also aligns with Eve’s concern about not pairing Alice and Bob together and leans on the only clean 3-player mission we’ve seen (Diana–Charlie–Eve) without reintroducing Charlie, who is under direct suspicion from M3. Overall, this lineup avoids the known suspicious pair, preserves the most trusted anchor, and gives us a new, informative test configuration.	\N	[-0.06303604,-0.018858567,-0.03510128,-0.063996084,0.017342342,0.04201172,0.028684199,-0.024202345,-0.053960845,0.06878626,-0.066317864,0.005923064,0.05106427,-0.061722133,0.0104289865,0.08891226,0.014200155,-0.012287102,0.00050080806,0.057467308,-0.11943583,-0.095441826,0.017465154,0.02966593,-0.0046626846,0.022261685,-0.005046405,0.020218406,-0.048369702,-0.16562158,0.006497357,0.0638053,0.071309224,0.024770869,-0.02884465,-0.0034687102,-0.01257118,-0.025234185,0.008162121,-0.042309243,0.03300374,-0.09216025,-0.016256053,-0.030544687,-0.062674835,0.024825428,0.02948371,0.022123761,0.0089651495,-0.014385245,-0.00028427577,-0.044152927,0.0015282921,0.00056048704,0.0039275326,0.04384659,-0.011341915,-0.0119401375,-0.005719375,0.031367972,0.027304478,0.08031011,-0.022884438,0.03627792,0.04130219,-0.01037772,-0.065381154,0.0203991,-0.0011911048,0.05032654,0.045258857,-0.031249056,-0.08096482,-0.07731456,-0.024870306,0.1411857,0.037688397,-0.07733006,0.056301285,-0.0075069778,-0.04701874,-0.052326273,0.0048228335,0.09331055,0.03079037,-0.013538698,-0.020871697,-0.063195646,0.011356449