191	avalon_20251130_234947	Diana	good	good	proposal	100400	100400	\N	The cleanest explanation of the results so far is that the Mission 2 and Mission 3 fails point toward Charlie and/or Eve, since each failed team added Eve to a previously successful Alice–Charlie pairing, and then a Diana–Eve team also failed. By contrast, Bob has only appeared on the one failed mission that already included the key suspects, and Alice has one prior success and only picked up a fail once Eve was added. Keeping both Charlie and Eve off the team is the most consistent way to avoid repeating past failure patterns, so the safest trio based on the available evidence is Alice, Bob, and Diana.	\N	[-0.03878145,-0.035164427,-0.02508256,-0.06525153,0.07424269,0.01781395,-0.03731434,-0.027554793,0.0069198767,0.07655539,0.008380593,0.016710842,0.067892596,-0.11300997,0.01980102,0.02738864,-0.01439433,0.018587185,-0.016918564,-0.041249663,-0.06693304,-0.06888728,0.05470553,0.04251034,-0.010127355,0.08226049,0.015201795,-0.035680436,-0.009023811,-0.09524588,0.011003761,0.037582826,0.036640573,0.0072160223,0.04669919,0.021666126,0.019851537,-0.03679002,0.017482823,0.0076185036,0.002885157,-0.030041585,0.007134227,-0.04824526,-0.02181083,-0.021737581,-0.012663996,0.0006089228,0.021083534,-0.031403422,-0.026478441,-0.04031937,-0.015454255,0.009548679,0.0042912145,-0.016950486,-0.045278862,0.0036445044,-0.020936737,0.012694091,0.027972009,0.052776217,-0.049280602,-0.001990608,0.102888696,0.05225391,-0.08754879,-0.09547674,0.0065373695,0.061764766,0.014863147,-0.03537601,-0.10193257,-0.054415688,-0.07076533,0.06838613,0.08559749,-0.008026895,0.0012468292,-0.051960614,-0.043137446,-0.12823085,-0.0041268812,0.12803684,0.010621456,-0.03565781,-0.08749371,-0.05028656,0.012529659,0.021556094,-0.055839196,-0.030079018,0.07593002,0.09188277,0.090425216,0.044760127,-0.0043845987,0.016039008,0.037666135,0.04529275,-0.047677107,0.0603531,0.027199011,-0.0669899,0.0554786,0.02722434,0.056202207,-0.07883876,0.049