33	avalon_20251201_005546	Charlie	good	good	proposal	100301	100301	\N	Mission 2 (Alice, Bob, Charlie) produced the only fail, so at least one of Alice or Bob is evil. As Charlie and knowing I’m good, the evil is in {Alice, Bob}. Building a 2‑person team from players who were not on the failed mission—Eve and Diana—maximizes the chance of a completely clean team by fully avoiding the known suspect block. Including Bob or Alice would force us to bring along a pool that definitely contains at least one evil, which is unnecessary risk when we have a viable alternative in Eve + Diana.	\N	[-0.014658948,0.02224982,-0.024058536,-0.047878996,0.009173274,-0.02329735,-0.012498748,-0.010658893,0.012198774,0.06326776,-0.041632574,-0.026846284,0.08357407,-0.059026532,0.019698525,0.0463558,0.010061892,0.037773233,0.014595523,0.010532555,-0.08942913,-0.06859705,-0.023912761,-0.015339886,-0.089008346,0.08617448,-0.04565229,-0.010930833,-0.031439483,-0.10817566,-0.023257097,0.031147376,0.03756873,0.044717144,0.056723002,0.0020564324,0.004948904,0.01922875,0.0042904625,-0.023758737,-0.0067971223,-0.023755094,-0.03617352,-0.024975466,-0.09150831,0.008010889,0.027629005,0.026934935,0.05657847,-0.053498596,-0.0095484955,0.004476871,0.013392253,-0.0016857253,0.040449694,-0.010134042,-0.06601554,0.013883848,-0.019851021,0.05598148,0.028256772,0.03320261,-0.02218532,0.013016413,0.0958353,-0.001456134,-0.07377571,0.003078211,-0.041847467,0.048581313,0.01727623,-0.027286667,-0.09700424,-0.06492562,-0.05007149,0.028592227,0.09621239,-0.05025755,0.08167401,0.025967194,-0.015106519,-0.08257426,0.016050331,0.094815396,0.01602944,-0.02951847,-0.025222464,-0.051351037,0.08582057,0.02760008,-0.061196193,-9.179665e-05,0.114996605,0.09825633,0.11739335,0.03491495,-0.030941078,0.007515972,-0.043151043,0.10227239,-0.06065792,0.014879772,0.027572056,-0.05440147,0.081960216,-0.03178866,0.070305616,-0.05148506,0.030997004,-0.0663231,0.110539965,-0.024345426,0.004974918,-0.023339236,0.02841896,0.004224268,0